{"tid":2365400,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"就到星期五～中環觀塘嘅朋友係時候一齊食Lunch啦","createTime":"2021-01-13T17:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T12:37:50.000Z","uid":258706,"like":42,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"8b8c9f76ea058e9b693801ac90384ae81ae451e2","tid":2365400,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T17:05:38.000Z","msg":"就到星期五～中環觀塘嘅朋友係時候一齊食Lunch啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1月15日一點準時入席，唔好遲到啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nh89wVa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNh89wVa.jpg&h=c3f22cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢次係2021年第一次Lunch聚啊，希望多D人出席到啦！<br />\n<br />\n我知大家呢排都好嬲，希望大家能夠將悲憤化為力量，透過記者畀外國知我地放棄，亦畀港共知繼續搞爛個制度係會有後果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣、旗幟、口號為記，怕高風險既打工仔可以改舉白紙、雨遮 <br />\n<span class=\"pink\">當日亦係梁烈士離世一年七個月嘅日子，大家亦都可以按情況默哀</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：今次午間活動同David無關 (佢亦冇可能同時去曬兩個地方)<br />\n<br />\nBTW，預計會有大量5毛入黎放負，話今時今日再抗爭已冇用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔肯提出建議<br />\n有心出席既人，請直接ignore刻意放負、分化、踐想去既人既留言 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">1.15 IFC / APM見</span>"},{"pid":"456358ea6b62012624973069b8357613ee0bf6e1","tid":2365400,"uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T17:48:32.000Z","msg":"1.15 見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef06da4922ebca513d461444fa8e052f52a43ae7","tid":2365400,"uid":191474,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T18:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油"},{"pid":"cbe4cdee54081f30d897deae4be8cd18fd097bf3","tid":2365400,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T18:04:36.000Z","msg":"竟然有活動